# lloyd-flanagan-word-count package

The latest build status at [Travis CI](http://travis-ci.org):    [![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/alflanagan/lloyd-flanagan-word-count.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/alflanagan/llloyd-flanagan-word-count)

This is a version of the word-count package from the Atom Flight Manual, which I'm using to test publishing a package. DO NOT USE! This package does nothing beyond what the tutorial package does, and will disappear soon.

![A screenshot of your package](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/69169/2290250/c35d867a-a017-11e3-86be-cd7c5bf3ff9b.gif)
